  "content_html": "<div class=\"rich-text\"><h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:40px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">ElNet LTP leakage current harmonics and more</span></span></h3></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Has a measurement accuracy of 0.2% (0.1% by special order).<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>1600 samples per wave (3 voltage waves + 4 current waves).<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Measurement of leakage current and current in the zero line.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Collecting energy data for 6 months.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Clock with foreign exchange rates.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Measuring harmonies up to the 64th harmony.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Support for multiple languages ​​including Hebrew<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Communication channels RS485 + TCP/IP built into the device.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Support for MODBUS/BACNET communication protocols.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Digital output programming.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>High quality 320X240 color graphic screen.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Graphical wave display and 3D harmonics display.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Simple and easy panel installation on the front of the board.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>TCP/IP communication, e-mail support, and WEB surfing to the device via a browser.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Structured data collection.</span></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:40px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Related products</span></span></h3></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:22px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:22px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Control Applications Ltd</span></span></span></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">making contact</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:left;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">Phone: +972-3-6474998</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">​</span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:left;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">Fax: +972-3-6474598</span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\"