    "ElNet LTP leakage current harmonics and more",
    "Has a measurement accuracy of 0.2% (0.1% by special order).\n1600 samples per wave (3 voltage waves + 4 current waves).\nMeasurement of leakage current and current in the zero line.\nCollecting energy data for 6 months.\nClock with foreign exchange rates.\nMeasuring harmonies up to the 64th harmony.\nSupport for multiple languages including Hebrew\nCommunication channels RS485 + TCP/IP built into the device.\nSupport for MODBUS/BACNET communication protocols.\nDigital output programming.\nHigh quality 320X240 color graphic screen.\nGraphical wave display and 3D harmonics display.\nSimple and easy panel installation on the front of the board.\nTCP/IP communication, e-mail support, and WEB surfing to the device via a browser.\nStructured data collection.",
